overview: MyNamePlates is the unchallenged online leader of name plates in the US. We offer dozens of desk name plates ideal for offices, churches, schools, hospitals, banks, and more. We are one of the alliances of SmartSign and take pride in our quality products which offer practical solutions to complex problems. Our product range includes desk nameplates, wall name plates, equipment name plates, teller signs, table-top tent signs, and name badges. Quickly customize one of our name plates and see how easy designing on browser-based software can be. Our online wizards let you see your design before you place your order. Whether you buy low-cost XpressPlates or our award-winning Obsidian Series, we don’t charge extra for adding your name, logo, changing colors, fonts, and text style. Our mission is to make it easy for you to order name plates. There are no hidden charges and we offer batch pricing. When you order nameplates for a series of offices, you get a real break on pricing. We also partner with non-profit organizations and offer nameplates at discounted rates.
